{"content": "I need to multiply 37a \u00d7 635 in base 11.\n\nFirst, let me convert to base 10 to calculate:\n- 37a\u2081\u2081 = 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 10\u00d711\u2070 = 3\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 10\u00d71 = 363 + 77 + 10 = 450\u2081\u2080\n- 635\u2081\u2081 = 6\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 5\u00d711\u2070 = 6\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 5\u00d71 = 726 + 33 + 5 = 764\u2081\u2080\n\nNow multiply in base 10:\n450 \u00d7 764 = 343,800\u2081\u2080\n\nNow convert 343,800\u2081\u2080 to base 11:\n343,800 \u00f7 11 = 31,254 remainder 6\n31,254 \u00f7 11 = 2,841 remainder 3\n2,841 \u00f7 11 = 258 remainder 3\n258 \u00f7 11 = 23 remainder 5\n23 \u00f7 11 = 2 remainder 1\n2 \u00f7 11 = 0 remainder 2\n\nReading the remainders from bottom to top: 215336\u2081\u2081\n\nLet me verify: 2\u00d711\u2075 + 1\u00d711\u2074 + 5\u00d711\u00b3 + 3\u00d711\u00b2 + 3\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070\n= 2\u00d7161,051 + 1\u00d714,641 + 5\u00d71,331 + 3\u00d7121 + 3\u00d711 + 6\n= 322,102 + 14,641 + 6,655 + 363 + 33 + 6\n= 343,800 \u2713\n\n215336", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 44, "completion_tokens": 476}